name: Oarfish
summary: A rare "doomsday fish," also known as an oarfish, has been found off the coast of Southern California. The discovery of the 12-foot-long fish, which is believed to be a harbinger of earthquakes, has excited scientists and sparked speculations. The oarfish, which is typically found in deep waters, was found near La Jolla Shores and is now being examined by researchers to determine why it surfaced. The appearance of the oarfish has also raised questions about its possible connection to the recent earthquake that struck the region.

name: Karol G
summary: The popular video game Fortnite has announced Karol G as the headliner for the fifth season of its in-game concert series, 'Fortnite Festival.' The Colombian singer will perform a playable concert, allowing players to interact and experience her music within the virtual world. This collaboration marks the continuation of Fortnite's successful partnership with top artists, bringing exclusive musical experiences to its vast player base. The concert is scheduled to take place this summer and will feature exclusive rewards and highly requested features, further enhancing the immersive experience for Fortnite fans.
